{"tid":2026801,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我之前是在財委會打工的，而我批錢的原則是：「幹你娘批爆」","createTime":"2020-05-21T07:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:35:56.000Z","uid":65371,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c55d53690ac8798aa2594ad8a573bbba1235cc67","tid":2026801,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:41:35.000Z","msg":"一開波就嗱嗱聲乜都唔問狂撳贊成掣，<br />\n，支持到連敵人都怕嘅時候你就贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我之前是在財委會打工的，而我批錢的原則是：<br />\n<br />\n「幹你娘批爆」<br />\n<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘批爆，老子才不管甚麼庫房虧損三小的，每次批的就是雞巴一大巴。10億批成20億，50億批成100億，救海馬公園送埋23條，跟把整個政府的錢全送給北大人沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，主席跑來跟我說，這個月庫房虧損200億，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"0ca555ebef6857625c206518a9e2f3086acde305","tid":2026801,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c95115aafbec551eba32db11c82d33800eff0e","tid":2026801,"uid":191309,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"你打緊乜嘢中文？睇唔明"},{"pid":"bf2c7a48a91a3de9f5175a12ad3846b825bc2dc8","tid":2026801,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c8094f5a10b658b96d89d98a41d0db9b6db410","tid":2026801,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係台灣潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b3c3f0abe4b89f3077b786d510a5cfa8080e6f","tid":2026801,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚似m記剷薯條果篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}